dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads for Calumet County, Wisconsin in 2016. [This data represents the centerlines of all roads in Calumet County. The data is used in nearly all aspects of the Land Information Office and is updated almost every day. Updates are performed using source documents (surveys, plats, etc) along with any available aerial imagery.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most recent version of this data, please visit: https://gis-calumet.hub.arcgis.com/
